	ACSP.NET is a lightweight and fast .NET web-framework based on MVC and OWIN
	<h3>Main features</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Based on MVC and MVVM patterns</li>
		<li>Comes as OWIN middleware</li>
		<li>Uses switchable IOC container for itself and controllers, views constructor injection (Simplify.DI)</li>
		<li>Mono-friendly</li>
		<li>Support async controllers</li>
		<li>Uses fast templates engine (Simplify.Templates)</li>
		<li>Supports controllers which can be run on any page</li>
		<li>Localization-friendly (supports templates, string table and data files localization by default)</li>
		<li>Mocking-friendly</li>
	</ul>
